attachments.text:
*Proposed Changes*

• Fixes <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/issues/8030|#8030>
• Added a loading state for the patient count to prevent showing 0 before the data is fully loaded.
• Improved conditional rendering to display a skeleton loader or loading state during data fetch.

@ohcnetwork/care-fe-code-reviewers

*Merge Checklist*

• Add specs that demonstrate bug / test a new feature.
• Update <https://docs.ohc.network|product documentation>.
• Ensure that UI text is kept in I18n files.
• Prep screenshot or demo video for changelog entry, and attach it to issue.
• Request for Peer Reviews
• Completion of QA

*Summary by CodeRabbit*

• *New Features*  
   • Enhanced loading state handling across various components by allowing count properties to be `null` when data is not available.  
   • Improved error handling for phone number inputs in patient management.
• *Bug Fixes*  
   • Refined logic for displaying counts in `CountBlock` to prevent invalid counts during loading states.  
   • Updated validation for working hours input in user management.
• *Documentation*  
   • Improved clarity in user notifications and error messages across components.
